H0.text: Which European town gave its name to a Treaty which symbolizes closer economic links between European countries. Maastricht

A4.text: The Treaty on European Union, commonly known as the Maastricht Treaty, is the foundation treaty of the European Union (EU).

A5.text: The Treaty was signed in the Netherlands, in the city of Maastricht.
